    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/06/125391187/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_5860624862022791601.png",
                "id": "talent1796",
                "key": "旋規設矩",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "旋規設矩"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">迸發掃描</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">迸發掃描</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雙方選擇行動前：</span>如果我方場上存在草原核或豐穰之核，則使其<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>-1，並<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span>我方牌庫頂部的1張卡牌。然後，造成所<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span>卡牌原本元素骰費用+1的<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1</span>（可疊加，最多疊加到3次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/06/125391187/5939d61b0bbbc9069caa164fbf967189_7696720413409479351.png",
                "id": "talent46600",
                "key": "畫則巧施",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "畫則巧施"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">梅赫拉克的助力</span>，生成2層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">迸發掃描</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">梅赫拉克的助力</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p>角色「普通攻擊」造成的傷害+1，且造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色普通攻擊後：</span>生成迸發掃描。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合：2</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">迸發掃描</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雙方選擇行動前：</span>如果我方場上存在草原核或豐穰之核，則使其<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>-1，並<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">捨棄</span>我方牌庫頂部的1張卡牌。然後，造成所<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">捨棄</span>卡牌原本元素骰費用+1的<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span>（可疊加，最多疊加到3次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/06/125391187/23c5b1ed3865c0fe1cc2409747bb043a_6910247960935069374.png",
                "id": "talent76607",
                "key": "繁繪隅穹",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "繁繪隅穹"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/06/125391187/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_3901009188983164504.png",
                "id": "talent9200",
                "key": "草元素傷害‧其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素傷害‧其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/06/125391187/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_9131068176750049946.png",
                "id": "talent33661",
                "key": "草元素傷害‧其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/06/125391187/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_6859372906874249595.png",
                "title": "草元素傷害‧其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span></p><p>透過行動牌或角色技能的效果，將行動牌從手牌或牌庫中棄置。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span></p><p>每回合結束階段，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合-1</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/06/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7230662413050906063.png",
